snippet.title: Ori and the Will of the Wisps - Official Gameplay Trailer | The Game Awards 2019
snippet.description: From the creators of the acclaimed action-platformer Ori and the Blind Forest comes the highly anticipated sequel, Ori and the Will of the Wisps. Embark on an all-new adventure in a vast and exotic world when it launches on March 11, 2020.
